;São Paulo Association of Art Critics Awards
The [[Associação Paulista dos Críticos de Artes]] (APCA) honors the best in the fields of stage acting (since 1956), music, literature, film, television, plastic arts (since 1972/1973), and radio (since 1980).<ref>http://www.apca.org.br/</ref>
